&lt;p&gt;The first time you see true “dustless” sanding, it feels like cheating. The room stays clear, your lungs don’t protest, and the surface looks better with each pass. I remember a Saturday morning in a small basement shop—coffee steaming, maple table top ready, and my playlist queued up—when a familiar dread crept in. I loved building things, but I hated the blizzard of dust that came with it. It wove into sweaters, clung to eyelashes, and added an hour of cleanup to every project. That day, I swapped my old hose for a snug-fitting antistatic one, dialed the vacuum to the sweet spot, and tried random orbital sanding with the vac hooked up. Ten minutes later, I realized I was breathing easier. The snowstorm never came.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/01.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/10/vacuum-hookup-for-dustless-orbital-sanding-random-orbital-sanding/cards/facebook/vacuum-hookup-for-dustless-orbital-sanding-random-orbital-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/10/vacuum-hookup-for-dustless-orbital-sanding-random-orbital-sanding/cards/facebook/vacuum-hookup-for-dustless-orbital-sanding-random-orbital-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/10/vacuum-hookup-for-dustless-orbital-sanding-random-orbital-sanding/cards/facebook/vacuum-hookup-for-dustless-orbital-sanding-random-orbital-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/10/vacuum-hookup-for-dustless-orbital-sanding-random-orbital-sanding/cards/instagram/vacuum-hookup-for-dustless-orbital-sanding-random-orbital-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/10/vacuum-hookup-for-dustless-orbital-sanding-random-orbital-sanding/cards/instagram/vacuum-hookup-for-dustless-orbital-sanding-random-orbital-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.c